               <msContents>
                  <summary>Maṣḥafa gǝnzat “Book of the Funeral Ritual”&#xD; I) Maṣḥafa gǝnzat “Book
                     of the Funeral Ritual” (fols. 4ra-154ra)&#xD; - Introduction (fols.
                     4ra-10va)&#xD; - Discourse of St Athanasius on death (fols. 10va-17va)&#xD; -
                     Maṣḥaf za-wäḍʾat ʾǝm-ʾIyarusalem “Book that Came from Jerusalem” (fols.
                     17va-25ra)&#xD; - Homily by St Jacob of Serug for the funeral of priests and
                     deacons (fols. 77va-92va)&#xD; - Homily by ʾabbā Salāmā, Metropolitan of
                     Ethiopia (fols. 96vb-99ra)&#xD; - Lǝfāfa ṣǝdq “Bandlet of Righteousness” (fols.
                     103va-106rb)&#xD; - Mangada samāy “Journey to Heaven” (fols.
                     106rb-108rb).</summary>
